name: OS-72-10
Lore: 'Pilot of Obsidian 10. Has served aboard the Conquest, the Thunderflare and the Executor. Not interested in advancing his rank as it would remove him from the pilot''s seat.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if any TIE). When piloting a TIE at a cloud sector, adds one battle destiny and makes that TIE immune to attrition < 4 (< 6 if Obsidian 10).',
